y email at mailto alsrooms lbl gov alsrooms lbl gov or by phone at 510 486 7666 ALS Apartment Reservation Request Form To request housing in the ALS Apartments please provide the following information Name Home institution Email address Telephone number Fax number Dates for which reservation is requested Check in mm dd yy Check out mm dd yy What kind of room are you requesting Single 70 00 night Double 40 00 night per person two beds room Approximate time of arrival in Berkeley This reservation is for how many people Please provide the name and telephone number of your local contact at Berkeley Lab Name Telephone number Does your visit involve working and or attending a meeting at the ALS Yes No Do you have any special requirements relating to housing in the ALS apartments Other Housing Users with other housing needs should contact their local host contact for assistance with finding short or long term accommodation The local contact will be able to provide information about the Berkeley area transportation school districts shopping etc Other excellent sources for information about available housing in the Bay area include the Housing section of the Flea Market want ads in the Berkeley Lab newspaper http www lbl gov Publications Currents Currents the UC Berkeley http www housing berkeley edu housing Department of Housing and Dining web pages These pages contain information about the housing services offered by UC Berkeley as well as listings for local hotels and motels several of which give discounts to UC Berkeley and Berkeley Lab staff and guests http www springstreet com n nd ss pgHome Homestore com a fee based housing and rental service that also provides detailed information about Bay area communities 
